offline SFT at matched target gain. This directly falsifies the universal claim that on-policy data itself is the primary stabilizer.\n","\n","### D. Conflict defeats retention\n","\n","In the direct-conflict setting, old and new performance cannot both be perfect because the same prompt is assigned two incompatible labels. Failure here is not evidence that one optimizer is poor; it demonstrates that no universal continual-learning rule can ignore task compatibility.\n","\n","## 7. Necessary extensions before publication\n","\n","For a publishable result, repeat with:\n","\n","- at least three seeds;\n","- Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct or a 3B model;\n","- a natural-language benchmark such as TRACE, ToolAlpaca, or knowledge injection;\n","- per-task backward transfer and average forgetting;\n","- KL drift from the pre-adaptation checkpoint;\n","- a true SDFT implementation using the demonstration-conditioned teacher distribution;\n","- GRPO or REINFORCE when an explicit verifier is available.\n","\n","The small experiment is intended to find the boundary cheaply. It is not sufficient by itself to claim that the large-model result fails.\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":15,"id":"626327a8","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.execute_input":"2026-07-24T21:26:19.797962Z","iopub.status.busy":"2026-07-24T21:26:19.797556Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-07-24T21:26:19.804882Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-07-24T21:26:19.803762Z"},"papermill":{"duration":0.03508,"end_time":"2026-07-24T21:26:19.806701+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-07-24T21:26:19.771621+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","output_type":"stream","text":["Outputs: [PosixPath('/kaggle/working/on_policy_cl_stress_test/novel_offline_sft_3'), PosixPath('/kaggle/working/on_policy_cl_stress_test/conflict_offline_sft_3'), PosixPath('/kaggle/working/on_policy_cl_stress_test/supported_iterative_on_policy_4'), PosixPath('/kaggle/working/on_policy_cl_stress_test/conflict_iterative_on_